message: Hi Bob, thanks for your interest in this exclusive product. Considering its exceptional quality and unique benefits, I'm prepared to offer it to you at $950000. I believe this price fairly reflects its value. Let me know if this works for you, and we can take it from there.

Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer and the quality of the product. However, considering my budget and alternative options available, I'm prepared to move forward at a price of $850000. Let me know if we can agree on this price.
